{
  "stem": "21437.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is Emile-- Emile Zola's.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Emile Zola's, that was about a one man-- that was a true story, I think, and he was sent to the-- to-- to Devil Island.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think it was Esterhazy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was somebody by the name of Esterhazy who accused him. maybe, it was as well-- it was made into a film, probably.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But most of the time-- I mean, anything if it had literary merit, I enjoyed reading it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I-- I-- I had a voracious-- as far as I can remember, voracious appetite for reading.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So this is-- this is how my-- how my-- how my whole family was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it was a way of life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You didn't-- I didn't know anything else, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went to-- the first school was the-- not far from Bytomska.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is what I would like to tell you a bit about, because till I-- before-- till before-- till before I started school, I was really very sheltered.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I led a very sheltered life as a small child, because I always went with an adult.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never went unaccompanied by an adult.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we happened to play, let's say, outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was in a yard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was enclosed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The yard was enclosed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we played there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I didn't go outside to the street, you know, just walk down the street by myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But once I had to start school, I had to sit for an exam because I was a little bit younger than the others.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And by the time I started school, I could read and write, because I had for about a year before a private teacher who prepared me for this.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I don't-- I couldn't say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I suppose about twice a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
